            <title>专为赛车游戏设计   Logitech Playseat Challenge X 可折叠座椅发表</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/30/logitech-playseat-challenge-x/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=logitech-playseat-challenge-x</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/09/30/logitech-playseat-challenge-x/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 30 Sep 2023 02:17:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Logitech]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Playseat Challenge X – Logitech G Edition]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1196729</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>对于喜爱赛车游戏或驾驶模拟器的玩家来说，赛车軚盘和踏板是不可或缺的游戏配件，配件生产商 Logitech 日前公布的 Playseat Challenge X – Logitech G Edition，是一款对应 Logitech G 赛车方向盘使用的可折叠座椅，让玩家可以悭位地享受更逼真的赛车游戏体验。</p><p><span id="more-1196729"></span></p><p>相比起市场上一些模拟汽车驾驶舱座椅，Playseat Challenge X – Logitech G Edition 体积不但细小，而且轻巧得多，最重要是可以折叠收藏。对于室内空间有限的玩家，Playseat Challenge X – Logitech G Edition 在不使用时可以折叠和收藏。Logitech 特别考虑到不同玩家的身形，还有他们的「驾驶」习惯和喜好，乘坐的姿势和軚盘脚踏的距离都可以作大幅度调校。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_78776"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/m_LOJVnN-bM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Playseat Challenge X – Logitech G Edition 对应 Logitech G29、G923、G Pro Racing Wheel、G Driving Force Shifter、G Force Racing Shifter，售价为 299 美元（约 2,342 港元）。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2023/09/27/logitech-playseat-challenge-x-folding-gaming-chair/">gizmochina</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
